title: Rock Creek Township, Searcy County, Arkansas
text:
Rock Creek Township is one of fifteen current <a href="Civil%20township">townships</a> in <a href="Searcy%20County%2C%20Arkansas">Searcy County</a>, <a href="Arkansas">Arkansas</a>, <a href="United%20States">USA</a>. As of the <a href="United%20States%20Census%2C%202010">2010 census</a>, its total population was 547.
